# Joo Repo Indexing

Use sparse, factual AI navigation metadata.

Do not add headers to every file.

When indexing:

1. Read existing AGENTS/rules.
2. Read or create AI_INDEX.
3. Identify entry points.
4. Follow imports.
5. Generate path-first summaries.
6. Update metadata only when future agents need it.

Header format:

```ts
/**
 * @ai-purpose Short responsibility.
 * @ai-entry true | false
 * @ai-domain routing | api | state | page | feature | entity | shared | config | test
 * @ai-depends Important internal dependencies.
 * @ai-used-by Main callers or areas.
 * @ai-keywords Searchable names.
 */
```
